<div id="pf4182" class="pf w51 h2f6" data-page-no="4182"><div class="pc pc4182 w51 h2f6"><div class="t m1578 xc4 h5 y2a54 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 2 January 8-14 </div><div class="t m482a xda ha y2a1f ff2 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">C:</div><div class="t m482b x61 ha y2a1f ff2 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">rran</div><div class="t m482c x5e ha y2a1f ff2 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ti</div><div class="t m482d x47 ha y2a1f ff2 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">on </div><div class="t m1406 x20 ha y2a1f ff2 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> </div><div class="t m1063 xe h5 y2195 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Thus saith the Lord, thy redeemer, </div><div class="t m241 xc4 h5 y203f ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and he that formed thee from the </div><div class="t me62 xc4 h5 y2198 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">womb, I am the Lord that maketh all </div><div class="t mf49 xc4 h5 y19aa ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">things; that stretcheth forth the </div><div class="t m1e1 xc4 h5 y1a88 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">heavens alone; that spreadeth abroad </div><div class="t m833 xc4 h5 y12ec ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the earth by myself&quot; (Isa. 44:24). </div><div class="t m37c x92 h35 y20dc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Genesis 1 and 2 contain the Creation </div><div class="t m482 xc4 h35 y1fc3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">story. Nonreligious people, and also </div><div class="t m70b xc4 h35 y1ed7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">much of the religious world regard this </div><div class="t m723 xc4 h35 y1c47 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">as a myth. Conservative Christians </div><div class="t m3cd xc4 h35 y196d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">accept this account.as </div><div class="t m166b x40 h35 y196d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> fact. </div><div class="t m7ca xc4 h35 y1f9e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Far-reaching doctrinal consequences </div><div class="t mb48 x0 h35 y632 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">result from a belief that the Creation </div><div class="t m211 xc4 h5 y1a23 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">account </div><div class="t m21b x36 h5 y1a23 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">is not literal. The </div><div class="t me1c x1a h35 y1ef9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">integrity of </div><div class="t m2dc xb4 h5 y18b5 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&apos;theiSabbata </div><div class="t m4ad x49 h35 y1dc1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">which is a memorial of </div><div class="t m1ae xc4 h5 y1e2c ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">GreatiMMIgpendent on an actual </div><div class="t m590 xc4 h5 y1e95 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">weeroftreathie activity. In addition to </div><div class="t m721 xc4 h5 y1a48 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">th</div><div class="t m14d2 xbd h5 y1a48 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">i</div><div class="t m2304 x4 h5 y1a48 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">rdirettdmTtiand </div><div class="t m105c x85 h35 y202e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">in Exodus 20, the </div><div class="t m5b0 xc4 h5 y1600 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">keeping  of the Sabbath </div><div class="t m816 x8e h35 y19fd ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">is urged </div><div class="t m7bf x3a h5 y19fd ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">both  </div><div class="t m66e x72 h5 y2195 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">by counsel and by example </div><div class="t mbb5 x72 h5 y203d ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">throughout the Scriptures. Jesus </div><div class="t ma54 x72 h35 y2198 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">accepted the Creation story as literal </div><div class="t m2ee x72 h35 y144a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and upheld the observance of the </div><div class="t ma7a x72 h35 y2062 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sabbath. Difficulties in interpreting </div><div class="t m3a1 x72 h35 y12ec ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Scriptures develop when the literal </div><div class="t m2e2 x72 h35 y20dc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">days of Creation are discounted. If the </div><div class="t m5a1 x72 h35 y1fc3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">days of Creation were long, indefinite </div><div class="t m7d1 x72 h35 y1ed7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">periods of time, the fossils could </div><div class="t m81e x72 h35 y1ef0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">represent the remains of plants and </div><div class="t mf1d x72 h35 y18dc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">animals that lived and died during </div><div class="t mb24 x72 h35 y1bf3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">these long periods of time. We then </div><div class="t mf22 x72 h35 y632 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">have problems concerning the origin </div><div class="t m23b x8f h35 y1a23 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of sin. The Bible account indicates that </div><div class="t ma14 x72 h35 y1dc1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sin started with Eve. With sin came </div><div class="t m552 x72 h35 y1e2c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">death. If the buried fossils </div><div class="t m118e x72 h35 y1e95 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">accumulated during long, indefinite </div><div class="t mce5 x8f h35 y194a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Creation days, we are confronted with </div><div class="t m5ea x8f h35 y1651 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">evidences of death prior to Eve&apos;s </div><div class="t m6c4 x8f h35 y186d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">creation. </div><div class="t m485 xb0 h35 y1f5a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The first two chapters of Genesis </div><div class="t m8be x8f h35 y11ab ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">give us a recital of actual happenings </div><div class="t m9ea x8f h35 y1e38 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">during a one-week Creation. These </div><div class="t m39c x8f h35 y21ca ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">chapters also tell us of God&apos;s great </div><div class="t m12b x8f h35 y176f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">creative power which is the basis of </div><div class="t m23e x8f h35 y1e88 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">worship. Because God is Creator, He </div><div class="t m5a5 x8f h35 y17f8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">is entitled to receive our worship and </div><div class="t m2ab x8f h35 y1edb ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">praise at all times, but especially on </div><div class="t m14f x8f h35 y136f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Sabbath. </div><div class="t m9b4 x72 h5 y1108 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m23f x8f h5 y1d59 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t mcf9 xbc h5 y1b71 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Beginning </div><div class="t md1 xbc h5 y1793 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Gen. 1:1) </div><div class="t m558 x8f h5 y1660 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m56d xbc h5 y1d5d ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Purpose </div><div class="t m66f x21 h5 y105b ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Isa. 43:7) </div><div class="t mb7 x8f h5 y1d5e ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t ma7 xbc h5 y17dc ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Method of Creation </div><div class="t md4 x21 h5 y1a2c ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Ps. 33:6, 9) </div><div class="t m1ce x8f h5 y1c97 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m1a3 x21 h5 yb51 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Time of Creation </div><div class="t m9b8 x21 h5 y2043 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Gen. 1:31; 2:2) </div><div class="t m8a8 x8f h5 y2159 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m649 x21 h5 y1906 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In His Image </div><div class="t m306 x21 h5 y2000 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Geri. 1:27) </div><div class="t m2ef x8f h5 y1b77 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t md2e x21 h5 y1820 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Results </div><div class="t m44 x21 h5 y1b79 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Gen. 1:31) </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
